flare multicore STATIC fast path (HttpServer.serve_static_multicore(resp,
num_workers=N), v0.7 Phase 1E). N pthread workers share one listener fd
(EPOLLEXCLUSIVE on Linux >= 4.5) and each runs run_reactor_loop_static_shared
against a pre-encoded StaticResponse. Per-request work collapses to recv +
_scan_content_length + memcpy(resp.bytes) + send -- no parser, no handler,
no Response struct allocation, no header lookups, no body re-serialisation.
Apples-to-apples shape against actix_web / hyper / axum's static-response
TFB plaintext setups. Worker count from FLARE_BENCH_WORKERS (default 4),
pinning from FLARE_BENCH_PIN (default 1). Version recorded in env.json as
the current git commit sha at bench time.
